Class UserEventHandlerTest

java.lang.Object
UserEventHandlerTest
public class UserEventHandlerTest
extends java.lang.Object
A test class for the EventHandler class. This class establishes a connection to the Mock Database and tests actions in EventHandler that all users can perform.
